****Compilation*****
Make sure you are in the src file folder of A2, then type "make" into the LXTerminal.

*********Running the program*******
The program will open. You will be asked if you want to choose to translae morse code to english 
or english to morse code.
Once you have mad your selection you can enter either letters and numbers or "."'s and "-"'s.

*You may quit at anytime by pressing 'q'.

****Known Limitations******
pressing ctrl + c will close the program at any time.